caption.p: Survival rates of dsGFP- or dsNcHig-treated non-viruliferous or viruliferous N. cincticeps. The microinjected N. cincticeps individuals ( n = 70) were maintained with rearing and daily observed for calculation of survival rates. The data were statistically analyzed from three biological repeats. P-values were estimated using a Studentâ€™s t-test.
